<H1>vi: Tip...</H1>

<P>As you are entering text, make sure that each sentence ends
with a fullstop followed by two or more spaces.  You can
then be sure of using <STRONG>vi</STRONG>'s editing commands to manipulate the
sentences in your text.</P>

<P>If necessary use <STRONG>vi</STRONG>'s 
<A HREF="../vi/ten.html">global replace command</A> to change sentence
endings that do not meet this convention.</P>

